*vlc-2.0.3 (19 Jul 2012)

  19 Jul 2012; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> +vlc-2.0.3.ebuild:
  version bump

  19 Jul 2012; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> vlc-2.0.9999.ebuild,
  vlc-9999.ebuild:
  fix ogg automagic, bug #422515 by Franz Fellner

